I"C<h3 id="site-selection">Site selection</h3>

<p>In some instances, after login, users will be prompted for site selection. Follow the steps as shown in the gif below.</p>

<p><img src="/img/gif/siteselect.gif" width="100%" /></p>

<p>After login;
Select current site from the selection, the name of the site will appear at left corner of the menu bar.
If wrong site selected, click on the name, list of available sites will po up then go ahead and select the appropriate site. If current site is not among the list, kindly contact data supervisor or the system admnistrator.</p>
